(745, 'en', 'apps', 'phpfox', '3.0.0beta3', 'as_a_developer_you_can_create_applications', 'As a developer you can create applications and add them to {site_name}, taking advantage of the existing user base. You host the application, which means that you are in full control of your server specifications.', 'As a developer you can create applications and add them to {site_name}, taking advantage of the existing user base. You host the application, which means that you are in full control of your server specifications.', 1316529523),
