(750, 'en', 'apps', 'phpfox', '3.0.0beta3', 'whenever_you_plan_on_using_our_api_you_must_first_request_a_token_in_order_to_request_a_token_you_need_a_unique_key_that_we_send_to_you_when_a_user_visits_your_app_from_an_iframe_on_our_site_we_pass_this_along_as_b_get_key_b', 'Whenever you plan on using our API you must first request a token. In order to request a token you need a unique key that we send to you when a user visits your APP from an iframe on our site. We pass this along as <b>$_GET[&#039;key&#039;]</b>.', 'Whenever you plan on using our API you must first request a token. In order to request a token you need a unique key that we send to you when a user visits your APP from an iframe on our site. We pass this along as <b>$_GET[''key'']</b>.', 1316529697),
