(3982, 'vi', 'core', 'phpfox', '2.0.0alpha3', 'setting_shorten_parsed_url_links', '<title>Shorten Parsed URL Links</title><info>If the option to parse URL strings to links is enabled then you can control how long the URL string should be before you shorten it.\r\n\r\n<b>Note:</b> Set to <b>0</b> to have no limit.</info>', '<title>Shorten Parsed URL Links</title><info>If the option to parse URL strings to links is enabled then you can control how long the URL string should be before you shorten it.\r\n\r\n<b>Note:</b> Set to <b>0</b> to have no limit.</info>', 1239104765),
